<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="R" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Rope" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Rope,</orth> cord, halter, cable: <cit><quote>we will not hand a r. more,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tmp 1.1.25" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. I, 1, 25</bibl></cit>. <emph>the r. of his destiny,</emph> 33 (== halter). <cit><quote>buy a --'s end</quote> <bibl n="shak. err 4.1.16" default="NO" valid="yes">Err. IV, 1, 16</bibl></cit> (for flogging). <bibl n="shak. err 4.1.16" default="NO" valid="yes">Err. IV, 1, 16</bibl> <bibl n="shak. err 4.1.16" default="NO" valid="yes">Err. IV, 1, 16</bibl> <bibl n="shak. err 4.1.16" default="NO" valid="yes">Err. IV, 1, 16</bibl> <bibl n="shak. err 4.1.16" default="NO" valid="yes">Err. IV, 1, 16</bibl> <bibl n="shak. err 4.4.12" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 4, 12</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. err 4.4.12" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 4, 12</bibl> <bibl n="shak. err 4.4.12" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 4, 12</bibl> <bibl n="shak. err 4.4.12" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 4, 12</bibl> <bibl n="shak. 1h6 1.3.53" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A I, 3, 53</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. rom 3.2.132" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. III, 2, 132</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. per 4.1.55" default="NO" valid="yes">Per. IV, 1, 55</bibl>. Unintelligible: <cit><quote>I see that men make --s in such a scarre that we'll forsake ourselves,</quote> <bibl n="shak. aww 4.2.38" default="NO" valid="yes">All's IV, 2, 38</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>